## SIP N SAVOR
A web app for viewing cocktails and getting their ingridients. It is using
a public API(https://www.thecocktaildb.com/api.php).
## Author
123ZOKzok
## Requirements
Access to  a computer or any other gadget.
Access to internet.
## Setup
Clone to this repo : git clone https://github.com/123ZOKzok/sip-n-savor.git or git@github.com:123ZOKzok/sip-n-savor.git 
Download zipped file.
Unzip the downloaded files in a folder of your choice.
open the `index.html` from the zipped file with any browser to run the application.
## Technology used
HTML - which was used to develop the structure off the pages.
CSS - which was used to style the User Interface.
JS - Used in interactivity of the application.
## live link
https://123zokzok.github.io/sip-n-savor/
